                                    <div>
                                        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--c-text);margin:0 0 1px;">GitHub — Community Edition</p>
                                        <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--c-muted);margin:0;">Issues, Changelog, Quellcode</p>
