                                </a>
                                <a href="https://payhip.com/b/4auSd" target="_blank" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px;background:rgba(29,158,117,.05);border:1px solid rgba(29,158,117,.2);border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;transition:background .12s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(29,158,117,.1)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(29,158,117,.05)'">
                                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c-accent)" stroke-width="1.8" style="width:16px;height:16px;flex-shrink:0;" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
